
     Levels are a way to judge one's experience.  In this world 
you will automatically receive a message announcing when you gain
a new level.  Every time that you level, you will be able to goto
the church and pray for stats. Players may achieve up to level 100.

     Players recieve 6 prayers for every level 01-25.
     Players recieve 5 prayers for every level 26-50.
     Players recieve 3 prayers for every level 51-75.
     Players recieve 2 prayers for every level 76-100.


 See also, 'help stats', 'help church', 'help dying','help classes'
           'help wish', 'help rankings', 'help alt level'.

